---
title: Sticky Teriyaki Tofu and Veg with Ginger and Spring Onion Rice
description: Zingy, sweet and an exciting addition to midweek meals, this Sticky Teriyaki Tofu and Veg comes with punchy Ginger and Spring Onion Rice.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF221121_R21_W03_UK_V12887-2_MB_Main_high-e5c7dd2d.jpg
